(## ? Module 1: Theoretical Foundations & Architecture) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(### 1.1 CS Theory & Definitions \(then how this repo implements each\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. **Retrieval-Augmented Generation \(RAG\)**) Tj
T*
(- Definition: a generation architecture that first retrieves relevant context from a corpus, then) Tj
T*
(conditions an LLM prompt on that context.) Tj
T*
(- In this repo:) Tj
T*
(  - Retrieval happens before generation in `RAGPipeline.answer` \(`rag.retrieve` span before) Tj
T*
(  `rag.generate`\).) Tj
T*
(    Source: `src/ask_my_docs/pipeline.py:53-64`) Tj
T*
(  - Retrieved chunks are passed to Ollama prompt construction as `[doc_id] chunk_text` blocks.) Tj
T*
(    Source: `src/ask_my_docs/llm/ollama.py:162-174`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2. **Hybrid Retrieval**) Tj
T*
(- Definition: combine lexical retrieval \(keyword/statistical\) and semantic retrieval \(embedding) Tj
T*
(similarity\).) Tj
T*
(- In this repo:) Tj
T*
(  - Lexical engine: `BM25Okapi`.) Tj
T*
(    Source: `src/ask_my_docs/retrieval/hybrid.py:13,198-200`) Tj
T*
(  - Semantic engine: FAISS `IndexFlatIP` with dense vectors.) Tj
T*
(    Source: `src/ask_my_docs/retrieval/hybrid.py:201`) Tj
T*
(  - Final score = weighted sum of normalized lexical + normalized semantic scores.) Tj
T*
(    Source: `src/ask_my_docs/retrieval/hybrid.py:114-121,350-353`) Tj
T*
(  - Default weights are `lexical_weight=0.45`, `semantic_weight=0.55`.) Tj
T*
(    Source: `src/ask_my_docs/settings.py:26-27`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3. **BM25 \(Best Matching 25\)**) Tj
T*
(- Definition: probabilistic ranking over tokenized text emphasizing term frequency and inverse) Tj
T*
(document frequency.) Tj
T*
(- In this repo:) Tj
T*
(  - Built from chunk token lists with `BM25Okapi\(tokenized_chunks\)`.) Tj
T*
(    Source: `src/ask_my_docs/retrieval/hybrid.py:198-200`) Tj
T*
(  - Query lexical scores from `self._bm25.get_scores\(tokenize\(query\)\)`.) Tj
T*
(    Source: `src/ask_my_docs/retrieval/hybrid.py:340`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4. **Vector Similarity Search \(FAISS IP\)**) Tj
T*
(- Definition: nearest-neighbor search in vector space using similarity metric \(inner product) Tj
T*
(here\).) Tj
T*
(- In this repo:) Tj
T*
(  - Query embedding searched with `self._faiss_index.search\(query_embedding[None, :], search_k\)`.) Tj
T*
(    Source: `src/ask_my_docs/retrieval/hybrid.py:344-346`) Tj
T*
(  - `search_k` heuristic is `min\(len\(chunks\), max\(k*4, k\)\)`.) Tj
T*
(    Source: `src/ask_my_docs/retrieval/hybrid.py:344`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5. **Deterministic Hash Embeddings**) Tj
T*
(- Definition: fixed embedding function from tokens to vector dimensions via hash, useful for) Tj
T*
(reproducibility/offline behavior.) Tj
T*
(- In this repo:) Tj
T*
(  - `HashingEmbedder.embed` uses `blake2b`, chooses index/sign, accumulates vector, then L2) Tj
T*
(  normalizes.) Tj
T*
(    Source: `src/ask_my_docs/retrieval/hybrid.py:67-87`) Tj
T*
(  - Embedding dimension is configured by `RetrievalConfig.embedding_dim` \(default `256`\).) Tj
T*
(    Source: `src/ask_my_docs/settings.py:28`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
ET
endstream
