(6. **Chunking**) Tj
T*
(- Definition: partition source docs into overlapping windows to improve retrieval granularity.) Tj
T*
(- In this repo:) Tj
T*
(  - Default chunk params: `chunk_size_tokens=120`, `chunk_overlap_tokens=20`.) Tj
T*
(    Source: `src/ask_my_docs/settings.py:23-24`) Tj
T*
(  - Chunk IDs follow `"{doc_id}::chunk-{n}"`; metadata stores `start_word`.) Tj
T*
(    Source: `src/ask_my_docs/retrieval/hybrid.py:99-108`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(7. **Object-Oriented + Dataclass Design**) Tj
T*
(- Definition:) Tj
T*
(  - OOP organizes behavior/state in classes.) Tj
T*
(  - Dataclasses provide lightweight typed records.) Tj
T*
(- In this repo:) Tj
T*
(  - OOP service classes: `HybridRetriever`, `OllamaGenerator`, `MetricsStore`, `RAGPipeline`.) Tj
T*
(    Source: `src/ask_my_docs/retrieval/hybrid.py:124`, `src/ask_my_docs/llm/ollama.py:98`,) Tj
T*
(    `src/ask_my_docs/observability/metrics_store.py:35`, `src/ask_my_docs/pipeline.py:23`) Tj
T*
(  - Dataclass records: `Document`, `Chunk`, `RetrievedChunk`, `RAGAnswer`, `RequestMetricRecord`,) Tj
T*
(  `EvalExample`, `EvalReport`.) Tj
T*
(    Source: `src/ask_my_docs/models.py:10,25,35,46`,) Tj
T*
(    `src/ask_my_docs/observability/metrics_store.py:15`, `src/ask_my_docs/evaluation/runner.py:16,25`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(8. **Observability \(Tracing + Metrics\)**) Tj
T*
(- Definition: collect operational telemetry for latency, costs, and quality signals.) Tj
T*
(- In this repo:) Tj
T*
(  - Tracing: OpenTelemetry exporter writes JSONL spans \(`name`, `trace_id`, `duration_ms`,) Tj
T*
(  `attributes`\).) Tj
T*
(    Source: `src/ask_my_docs/observability/tracing.py:18-44`) Tj
T*
(  - Request metrics: DuckDB table `rag_request_metrics` captures latency/tokens/cost/quality fields.) Tj
T*
(    Source: `src/ask_my_docs/observability/metrics_store.py:69-85`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(9. **Regression Gating**) Tj
T*
(- Definition: fail deployment/CI when quality drops or latency/cost worsens beyond policy.) Tj
T*
(- In this repo:) Tj
T*
(  - Gate config model in YAML: absolute + regression blocks.) Tj
T*
(    Source: `configs/regression_thresholds.yaml:1-11`, `src/ask_my_docs/evaluation/gating.py:12-31`) Tj
T*
(  - Gate eval compares current metrics to absolute bounds and optional baseline deltas.) Tj
T*
(    Source: `src/ask_my_docs/evaluation/gating.py:52-124`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(10. **Privacy-by-default Question Storage**) Tj
T*
(- Definition: avoid storing raw user input unless explicitly enabled.) Tj
T*
(- In this repo:) Tj
T*
(  - `observability_store_raw_questions=False` default.) Tj
T*
(    Source: `src/ask_my_docs/settings.py:55`) Tj
T*
(  - Question is hashed/redacted as `<redacted:sha256:{digest}:len={n}>` unless enabled.) Tj
T*
(    Source: `src/ask_my_docs/pipeline.py:150-154`) Tj
T*
(  - Verified by tests.) Tj
T*
(    Source: `tests/test_pipeline.py:55,68,82`) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
