T*
(`tests/test_metrics_store.py:36-38,88-89`.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(#### Scenario 2 Answer \(model discovery instability\)) Tj
T*
(Current behavior:) Tj
T*
(- parse rows from `ollama list`.) Tj
T*
(- prefer configured model if present.) Tj
T*
(- else prefer first local model \(`size != "-"`\).) Tj
T*
(- timeout raises runtime error.) Tj
T*
(Enhancements:) Tj
T*
